<div class="content">
<div class="container intro">
    <h3 class="intro-heading" href=""> Hello, <%= name %></h3>
    <h5 class="intro-id ">UserId: <%= userId %></h5> <br>
    <p class="intro-text">Dionysus is a movie recommendation system that uses a MovieAPI and recommends movies based 
        on the data it has been trained on. The website is a presentation of those recommendations in addition to 
        a content-based recommendation system. You, the anonymous, can check recommendations for 600 other users who have rated
        the movies in our dataset by entering any random userId. 
    </p>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <form action="" method="POST">
                <input type="text" name="userid" class="id form-control" placeholder="UserId" autocomplete="off">
                <span class="help-block">Enter any random userId between 0 and 610 or else land on 404</span>
                <button type="submit" style="display: none;"></button>
            </form>
        </div>
